Code 

class Solution {
    public TreeNode invertTree(TreeNode root) {
        if(root == null) return null;

        TreeNode temp = root.right;
        root.right = root.left;
        root.left = temp;

        invertTree(root.left);
        invertTree(root.right);

        return root;
    }
}

Time Complexity : O(n)
Space Complexity : O(log n) Balanced Tree
                   O(n)
